### Register a new user
POST http://localhost:5000/api/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "email": "testuser@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Login and get JWT token (returns access + refresh)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Select character (Protected)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/select-character
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "characterId": 1
}

### Get all users (Public for now)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

### Get lobby info (Protected)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/lobby
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Get profile info (Protected)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Refresh access token using refreshToken cookie
POST http://localhost:5000/api/refresh-token
